# Privacy Policy for Nifty Analytica

**Effective Date: May 21, 2025**

Nifty Analytica ("we," "us") values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle data in our mobile app, Nifty Analytica (the "App"). By using the App, you agree to this policy.

## Information We Collect

We collect minimal, non-personal data:
- **Device Information**: Device type and OS version to ensure App functionality.
- **Usage Data**: Anonymized analytics (e.g., feature usage) to improve the App.
- **Crash Reports**: Anonymized error data to fix issues.

We do not collect personal information (e.g., name, email).

## How We Use Data

We use data to:
- Deliver stock market analytics via internet connectivity.
- Enhance App performance and user experience.
- Fix technical issues.

## Data Sharing

We do not sell or share your data, except:
- **Analytics Providers**: Anonymized data with services like Firebase (see [Firebase Privacy](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)).
- **Legal Obligations**: If required by law.

## Data Security

We use reasonable measures (e.g., encryption) to protect data, but no system is fully secure.

## Your Choices

Disable analytics via device settings or contact us.

## Children’s Privacy

The App is not for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect their data.

## Changes

We may update this policy and notify you via the App. Check [your-website.com/privacy] for updates.

## Contact

Questions? Email us at shivrajsys@gmail.com.

